metadata.name: A time to reflect.
metadata.description:
This is my SuperRare Genesis piece part 1. I wanted to pick a photo that really spoke to me on a personal level and represents who i am as an Artist / Photographer. 
This photo reflects a changing world coming out of a global pandemic and the civil rights movement of 2020-2021. 
Street Photography and street portraits are one of my most passionate things to shoot. This mint is the first time i have shared this photo with the world. I hope you enjoy.
